title: Cyanogenmod S4 Active 4.3.1 20140218 jactiveltexx
description:
It's for the INTERNATIONAL version (i9295). 
It's NOT for the USA-only, AT&T proprietary, locked bootloader-version (i537).


Instructions (for updating from previous CM-version:
-------------

1. Put ZIP-file on internal or external card. (Don't extract anything!)
2. Boot into recovery mode.
3. Install ZIP.
4. Format Cache. (All apps, pics, personal data etc will be safe and remain intact.)
5. Reboot.
